OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FA tale of two earthquakes: 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FHow Taiwan learnt from past
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fdisaster                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, When disasters happen, particularly    
OL,6, when big earthquakes strike, the       
OL,7, world's media is drawn like flies to   
OL,8, the most dramatic destruction. It is   
OL,9, understandable. But it often portrays a
OL,10, distorted picture of what has happened.
OL,12,FYou can see it here in the city of     
OL,13,FHualien. Camera teams are crowded      
OL,14,Faround a 10-storey building leaning    
OL,15,Fover at a terrifying angle. It all     
OL,16,Flooks bizarre and scary. But that was  
OL,17,Fonly one of a handful of buildings     
OL,18,Fwhich suffered structurally, in a city 
OL,19,Fof tens of thousands.                  
